---
title: Shallot Peppercorn Pork Chops with Braised Cabbage and Crispy Potatoes
description: These chops will leave you feeling like you’ve just left a pricey Parisian bistro. Finished with a French-inspired peppercorn sauce, these juicy chops are total date-night material. Served with buttery cabbage and crispy potatoes, you’ll be making this recipe for every special occasion.
